1. *Brinu* me mnoge obaveze. (I am *worried* about many obligations.)
2. Njih *brinu* finansijski problemi. (They are *concerned* about financial problems.)
3. Ne treba da se *brineš* oko toga. (You don't need to *worry* about that.)
4. *Brinuo* se za svaku sitnicu. (He *fretted* over every little thing.)
5. *Brinuli* su o njegovom zdravlju. (They *cared* about his health.)
6. Ne *brini* se, sve će biti u redu. (Don't *worry*, everything will be fine.)
7. Oni se *brinu* da će izgubiti posao. (They are *worried* about losing their job.)
8. Molim te, *brini* o svom zdravlju. (Please, *take care* of your health.)
9. Oni *brinu* o deci kao da su im sopstvena. (They *care* for the children as if they were their own.)
10. *Brinuti* o drugima je vrlo važno. (*Taking care* of others is very important.)